<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tʿbt mn ạlḍyạʿ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- tʿbt mn ạlḍyạʿ krht ạlbʿd wṭʿm ạlgẖrbẗ
 tʿbt mn ạlḍyạʿ wʿm ftsẖ ʿly̱ rạḥẗ qlby
 tʿbt mn ạlḍyạʿ msẖ ʿm bqdr lạqy ḥạly
 tʿbt mn ạlḍyạʿ wrḥ ạ̉ṣrkẖ bạlṣwt ạlʿạly
 ạlqrạr - yạrb ạ̹rḥmny wkẖlṣny slạmk wḥdh bynqṣny
 bʿdt ktyr rjʿt btwbẗ ạ̉nạ kẖạṭy ạrḥmny wkẖlṣny
 2- krht ạlmạḍy wạ̉kẖbạrh wshr ạllyl wạ̉srạrh
 wạlly kạnwạ sbb lfrḥy ạ̉sbạb ạlḥzn ṣạrwạ
 kdẖb wskr wlʿb qmạr wsẖr msyṭr ʿạlạ̉fkạr
 wạlmkẖdr lyl nhạr yṭbʿ fyy ậtẖạrh
 btrjạk tṭlʿ fyy ḥbl ạlmwt ạltf ʿlyy
 wạlly fkrth ạlḥryẗ ʿm yṣlbny bmsmạrh
 3- ʿmry bạ̹ydy ḍyʿth wrḥ tṭlb mny ḥsạbh
 wjsmy ạlly bạ̹ydyk ʿjnth bkrạ byrjʿ ltrạbh
 ạ̉nạ bʿrf ạ̹ny ạlmsỷwl lkn mạ fy ʿndy ḥlwl
 msẖ ʿạrf sẖw bdy qwl wậmạly kln kẖạbwạ
 mạ bstạhl qlk byy klmẗ byy kbyrẗ ʿly
 tʿbt ktyr mn ạlkẖṭyẗ wqlby tmrmr bʿdẖạbh</lyrics>
<author>ạ̉ymn kfrwny, ạ̉ymn kfrwny</author>
<hymn_number>2056</hymn_number>
</song>